<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA11">
<l>nāḻā lamarmuyaṉṟa vallarakka ṉiṉṉuyirai</l>
<l>vāḻā vakaivalita ṉiṉvaliyē yāḻāta</l>
<l>pārunī vāṉunī kālunī tīyunī</l>
<l>nīrunī yāyniṉṟa nī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it strength in you to force, in a manner that he did not live,</l>
<l>the sweet life of the strong Rakṣasa who by [his own] fault exerted himself in battle,</l>
<l>you who stand as uncrying earth, you as sky, you as wind,</l>
<l>you as fire and you as water?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
